"{\"uid\": \"oikoumene.org-news-on-behalf-of-global-christian-fellowship-wcc-calls-for-explanation-of-olympics-opening-ceremony\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"World Council of Churches general secretary Rev.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 48, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Churches\", \"from\": 17, \"to\": 25}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Prof. Dr Jerry Pillay, in a letter to the International Olympic Committee and the French Olympic Committee, urgently called for an explanation of what has been perceived as a depiction of the Last Supper during the Olympics opening ceremony.\", \"from\": 49, \"to\": 290, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 91, \"end\": 122, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"International Olympic Committee\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 131, \"end\": 155, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_National_Olympic_and_Sports_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"French Olympic Committee\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_National_Olympic_and_Sports_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_National_Olympic_and_Sports_Committee\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Prof. Dr Jerry Pillay\", \"from\": 49, \"to\": 70}, {\"ngram\": \"a letter\", \"from\": 75, \"to\": 83}, {\"ngram\": \"an explanation\", \"from\": 177, \"to\": 191}, {\"ngram\": \"a depiction\", \"from\": 222, \"to\": 233}, {\"ngram\": \"the Last Supper\", \"from\": 237, \"to\": 252}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics opening ceremony\", \"from\": 260, \"to\": 289}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Share this article \\\"In particular, it has angered many Christians who are disgusted and appalled by the mockery of the Christian faith as depicted in what is considered to be a portrayal of the Lord's Last Supper,\\\" wrote Pillay.\", \"from\": 292, \"to\": 521, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 348, \"end\": 358, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christians\", \"score\": 0.5446323549552641, \"rank\": 0.5022845611032495, \"text\": \"Christians\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christians\"}, {\"begin\": 412, \"end\": 421, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"score\": 0.8285914406465744, \"rank\": 0.20686728526160986, \"text\": \"Christian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this article\", \"from\": 298, \"to\": 310}, {\"ngram\": \"the mockery\", \"from\": 392, \"to\": 403}, {\"ngram\": \"a portrayal\", \"from\": 467, \"to\": 478}, {\"ngram\": \"the Lord's Last Supper\", \"from\": 482, \"to\": 504}, {\"ngram\": \"Pillay\", \"from\": 513, \"to\": 519}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The World Council of Churches would like you to explain to us in detail the use of this idea and whether it was intended in any way to refer to the Christian faith.\\\"\", \"from\": 521, \"to\": 687, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 670, \"end\": 679, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"score\": 0.8285914406465744, \"rank\": 0.20686728526160986, \"text\": \"Christian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The World Council\", \"from\": 522, \"to\": 539}, {\"ngram\": \"Churches\", \"from\": 543, \"to\": 551}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 581, \"to\": 583}, {\"ngram\": \"detail\", \"from\": 587, \"to\": 593}, {\"ngram\": \"the use\", \"from\": 594, \"to\": 601}, {\"ngram\": \"this idea\", \"from\": 605, \"to\": 614}, {\"ngram\": \"any way\", \"from\": 646, \"to\": 653}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Pillay reflected that the Last Supper is essential to Christian beliefs and practice and any form of mockery shows the highest form of disrespect and insensitivity.\", \"from\": 691, \"to\": 855, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 745, \"end\": 754, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"score\": 0.8285914406465744, \"rank\": 0.20686728526160986, \"text\": \"Christian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Pillay\", \"from\": 691, \"to\": 697}, {\"ngram\": \"the Last Supper\", \"from\": 713, \"to\": 728}, {\"ngram\": \"practice\", \"from\": 767, \"to\": 775}, {\"ngram\": \"any form\", \"from\": 780, \"to\": 788}, {\"ngram\": \"mockery\", \"from\": 792, \"to\": 799}, {\"ngram\": \"the highest form\", \"from\": 806, \"to\": 822}, {\"ngram\": \"disrespect\", \"from\": 826, \"to\": 836}, {\"ngram\": \"insensitivity\", \"from\": 841, \"to\": 854}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The WCC is represented by 352 member churches with over 600 million Christians in the world,\\\" Pillay wrote.\", \"from\": 859, \"to\": 967, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 928, \"end\": 938, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christians\", \"score\": 0.5446323549552641, \"rank\": 0.5022845611032495, \"text\": \"Christians\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christians\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The WCC\", \"from\": 860, \"to\": 867}, {\"ngram\": \"352 member churches\", \"from\": 886, \"to\": 905}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 942, \"to\": 951}, {\"ngram\": \"Pillay\", \"from\": 954, \"to\": 960}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"As the largest ecumenical fellowship in the world, we have a responsibility to respond to the concerns of Christians raised about the perceived mockery of the Christian faith in the Last Supper scene in the ceremony, and thus request your immediate response to our request.\\\"\", \"from\": 967, \"to\": 1242, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1074, \"end\": 1084, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christians\", \"score\": 0.5446323549552641, \"rank\": 0.5022845611032495, \"text\": \"Christians\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christians\"}, {\"begin\": 1127, \"end\": 1136, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"score\": 0.8285914406465744, \"rank\": 0.20686728526160986, \"text\": \"Christian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the largest ecumenical fellowship\", \"from\": 971, \"to\": 1004}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 1008, \"to\": 1017}, {\"ngram\": \"a responsibility\", \"from\": 1027, \"to\": 1043}, {\"ngram\": \"the concerns\", \"from\": 1058, \"to\": 1070}, {\"ngram\": \"the perceived mockery\", \"from\": 1098, \"to\": 1119}, {\"ngram\": \"the Last Supper scene\", \"from\": 1146, \"to\": 1167}, {\"ngram\": \"the ceremony\", \"from\": 1171, \"to\": 1183}, {\"ngram\": \"your immediate response\", \"from\": 1202, \"to\": 1225}, {\"ngram\": \"our request\", \"from\": 1229, \"to\": 1240}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Read the full letter \\\"In lead-up to Olympics, Paris churches are showing they care\\\" - WCC feature story, 25 July 2024) Please fill in this form if you would like to receive news and updates from the WCC by email.\", \"from\": 1244, \"to\": 1458, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1291, \"end\": 1296, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.999967970410356, \"rank\": 3.20306155344628e-05, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the full letter\", \"from\": 1249, \"to\": 1264}, {\"ngram\": \"lead-up\", \"from\":